{"tid":967064,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【請停手吧】「C.朗」下面已被摸到發光...","createTime":"2019-01-03T08:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T07:42:46.000Z","uid":29540,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fe900337067fca69a3f80d045fa203f5327d3fdf","tid":967064,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:49:13.000Z","msg":"在翻閱英國媒體的時候，赫然看到一個標題：《Golden Balls！ Cristiano Ronaldo &hellip;&hellip;》。一瞬間還以為C.朗拿度要得金球獎了，點進去一看，原來標題的意思是C.朗拿度多了一對金色的蛋蛋。<br />\n<br />\n　　所有人都知道，C.朗拿度有座銅像，和他本人一樣知名。但這次的主角不是那座醜哭了的銅像，因為那一座只有上半身。<br />\n<br />\n　　今天要說的是這座C.朗拿度的全身像，它位於C.朗拿度家鄉的馬德拉CR7酒店，2014年問世以來，就成了這座城市的標誌物之一。如果你我有機會路過，肯定也會忍不住與雕像合一張影。<br />\n<br />\n　　不過！與所有城市或旅遊景點的銅像一樣，C.朗拿度也難逃遊客們的毒手&hellip;&hellip;通過最新的照片可以清晰的看到，C.朗拿度銅像的某些部位有了磨損，除了雙手，最亮眼的就是兩腿之間的那個位置。<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/01/03/4/46a6cc5208157eaad8de68eec4124caf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F01%2F03%2F4%2F46a6cc5208157eaad8de68eec4124caf.jpg&h=b6765fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　C.朗拿度銅像的下面顏色鮮明，閃閃發光，又鼓又亮&hellip;&hellip;為什麼會變成這樣？也不用多說了吧，因為遊客們都是這麼玩的：<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/01/03/f/f970a7afa15a4aaf84ad308584ffc3b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F01%2F03%2Ff%2Ff970a7afa15a4aaf84ad308584ffc3b4.jpg&h=7cf6e38b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　不知C.朗看到女遊客們如此撫摸他的敏感部位作何感想，更不知他看到銅像鋥光瓦亮的凸起時會是什麼無語的表情。<br />\n<br />\n　　與C.朗拿度一樣，大衛碧咸的雕像也被不少女性愛撫過，稍微好一點的是，碧咸的雕像不會掉色。<br />\n<br />\n　　C.朗拿度的銅像還算幸運，雖然失了點貞操，但至少保住了性命。美斯也有一座銅像，坐落在阿根廷首都布宜諾斯艾利斯的榮譽大道上，後來直接被人推倒，現在只剩下一雙盤帶的腿，而且壞了一年都沒能修復，有關部門的回應也很實誠：沒錢修。<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/01/03/9/987ae1c195556b820c21bb83fd14a6f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F01%2F03%2F9%2F987ae1c195556b820c21bb83fd14a6f4.jpg&h=aaee5d93&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/01/03/8/877325b44c917f6f6761c2376d080eed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F01%2F03%2F8%2F877325b44c917f6f6761c2376d080eed.jpg&h=5e2a338a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/01/03/7/7843e01fdeebc528f71e2be262963359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F01%2F03%2F7%2F7843e01fdeebc528f71e2be262963359.jpg&h=c347550d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079f75540b7f4bf5e13b5cc837b2607e9964c785","tid":967064,"uid":34553,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25df5d03e1eb8b7acb334454db8b65f322c1305c","tid":967064,"uid":70013,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:05:52.000Z","msg":"美斯嗰個笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb35198ac45f897df748fe08b19eb332aca277b0","tid":967064,"uid":734,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"條丁跟朴智星整嫁？整到咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3krHxCg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3krHxCg.gif&h=7eb485cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f8f81817f5ca23eef2006aa1ba1a6d420956669","tid":967064,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"25df5d03e1eb8b7acb334454db8b65f322c1305c","tid":967064,"uid":70013,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:05:52.000Z","msg":"美斯嗰個笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" cl